# Implement from handoff mode

When this rule applies (user @-mentions it or says **Implement handoff** / **Coding agent**):

1. Follow project skill **`coding-agent`** (`.cursor/skills/coding-agent/SKILL.md`) — includes handoff rules from **`implement-from-handoff`**.
2. Read `.agents/handoffs/LATEST.md` before editing code.
3. Implement only what the handoff specifies; respect out-of-scope and acceptance criteria; run deslop after iteration 1.

Prefer **`@coding-agent-mode`** for the same behavior. For full agent roster, see `AGENTS.md`.
